<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Upper left part of a <rs type="material">white marble</rs> panel, probably the side of a <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.17</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.695</measure>  × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.17</measure>).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>Inscribed on one face, l.2 ff. within a moulded panel (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre" precision="circa">1.07</measure> x <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.56</measure>) , and, l.1, on its upper border (0.94 x 0.04) which is chipped at the upper left corner. The upper end was re-cut in the Byzantine period, with elaborate patterns, and painted.
</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.03</measure>; several ligatures</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0200" exact="none">Second century A.D.</date>
 (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)</p>
</div>
